msgctxt "After00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>We've traveled for months in search of\n"
"a flower called the <2.se_co>silent princess<3.re_co>.<4.ra>Legend has it"
" that if you swear your love\n"
"before its freshly plucked blossom, you\n"
"and your partner will live a charmed life.\n"
"<5.so>Alas, all our searching so far has been\n"
"for naught."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Atacked00"
msgid "<1.so>Sorelia! Run, quickly!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Atacked01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I can't stand constantly being driven\n"
"off this way!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Failed00"
msgid "<1.so>Heavens... <2.pa>That was a narrow escape."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Failed01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Curse my weakness for letting that thing\n"
"get the better of me..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: raw
#. 4: sound
msgctxt "GoodBye00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I suppose no place in Hyrule is safe\n"
"anymore.<2.pa> Not even the settlements.<3.ra><4.so>All the more reason "
"for me to redouble\n"
"my training in order to help my beloved\n"
"Sorelia!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Guardian00"
msgid "<1.so>Run away! The Guardian is coming!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: raw
#. 5: sound
msgctxt "Meeting00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I wanted to find a still-living\n"
"<2.se_co>silent princess<3.re_co>, which we know\n"
"only through the tales.<4.ra>I intended to set out on my own, but\n"
"Sorelia would have none of it and\n"
"insisted on coming along.\n"
"<5.so>I felt confident enough in my skill with\n"
"a blade to protect myself, but I need to\n"
"reconsider that to keep my beloved safe."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Meeting02"
msgid "<1.so>I'm happy just to be together with you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Meeting03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sorelia... I won't allow any misfortune to\n"
"befall you! I swear it!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Near00"
msgid "<1.so>I'm saved..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Near01"
msgid "Sorelia..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "PairAtacked00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sorelia! Stand fast! I'm coming to\n"
"save you!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "PairAtacked01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Please help my wife! She's still in danger\n"
"from those monsters!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "PairFailed00"
msgid "<1.so>Sorelia... Please be all right..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "PairFailed01"
msgid "<1.so>No... This can't be happening!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv1_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You saved not just me but my wife, as\n"
"well. <2.pa>We can't spare much, but we owe\n"
"you this, at least."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv1_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Is my wife safe, as well? <2.pa>Oh, thank\n"
"heavens. <3.pa>I don't know how I'd go on\n"
"living without her."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv2_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You've done what neither my wife nor\n"
"I could have, and we're alive as a result.\n"
"Thank you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv2_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Do you wander Hyrule keeping everyone\n"
"safe? <2.pa>You're doing good work. <3.pa>Here,\n"
"this is to show my appreciation."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "SavedLv3_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It's a miracle that you stepped in to\n"
"save us. <2.pa>Let me do this much for you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "SavedLv3_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>There aren't many heroes in the world\n"
"like you anymore. I think Sorelia and I\n"
"can part with this as a thank-you gift."
msgstr ""

